Author: RosieNP
Text: That's a much healthier was to get there. Preserve your recovery...  you likely worked hard for it.

Author: dgracieh
Text: I feel like a pound a week is still slightly rapid. I’m not a medical professional but I’ve been declining since I last left treatment at my set point and have lost about 2 pounds a week continuously and just from the way my therapist reacts every week when she sees this, I don’t think it’s considered normal/healthy weight loss. Please stay safe!!
